snippet.title: G.I. Joe: Wrath of Cobra - Official Reveal Trailer | The MIX Next August 2023
snippet.description: Check out the reveal trailer for GI Joe: Wrath of Cobra for a peek at gameplay and more from the upcoming game. GI Joe: Wrath of Cobra will be available in 2024.
